title: ASUS finally brings the ROG Phone 5s and ROG Phone 5s Pro to the Indian market
content:
ASUS refreshed its ROG Phone 5 gaming smartphone lineup in August last year with two new models — the ROG Phone 5s and the ROG Phone 5s Pro.
